timeline.bodyText:
What do you want from its value type and why this condition may accept random data types? These constants aren't fixed in H2, they may be modified at any time.
Use
String nullString = null;
if (v2 != null) {
    nullString = v2.getString();
}
as it was suggested earlier. Additional checks not worth here.

